OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Frain through the evening and overnight
OL,7,Fbut some drier weather spreading from
OL,8,Fthe west towards morning. Rain turning
OL,9,Fto snow over the Southern Uplands
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FCloudy morning with rain and
OL,13,Fhill snow in the east. Dry conditions
OL,14,Fat first in the west will spread to
OL,15,Fall areas through the day with
OL,16,Fincreasing bright spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
